date: Tue Feb 08 2022 04:02:14 GMT+1100 (Australian Eastern Daylight Time)
keywords: Bob Carr,Peter Dutton,bob carr peter dutton
description: Bob Carr has doubled down on his claim that Peter Dutton called the Prime Minister an 'absolute psycho' on Sunday night. Mr Carr alleged in a tweet that it was the defence minister who shared the text exchange with then NSW premier Gladys Berejiklian during the 2019-20 bushfire crisis. Mr Dutton angrily denied the claim, saying it was 'baseless, untrue and should be deleted'
metaDescription: AI generated image of Bob Car who involved in a twitter war over the text exchange with then NSW premier Gladys Berejiklian during the 2019-20 bushfire crisis.
